%section#partners.py-5
  %h5.text-muted.mb-3.text-center Partners & Contributors
  %h2.fw-bold.text-center Working Together to Power Alaska
  %p.lead.text-muted.text-center.mb-5
    Many organizations have shaped the development and the data presented in the AEDG. Learn more about them here.

  - grouped_partners.each do |category, partners|
    %h4.mt-5.mb-4.text-muted= category.titleize
    .row
      - partners.each do |partner|
        .col.col-sm-6.col-lg-3.mb-4
          = link_to partner['url'], target: "_blank", class: "d-block p-4 bg-white border rounded shadow-sm text-decoration-none text-dark h-100 hover-shadow text-center" do
            .d-flex.flex-column.align-items-center.justify-content-center.h-100
              / Logo container with fixed size
              .logo-wrapper.mb-3{ style: "width: auto; height: 90px;" }
                - if partner['logo']
                  = image_tag "partners/#{partner['logo']}", class: "img-fluid object-fit-contain h-100", alt: partner['name']
                - else
                  = image_tag "https://placehold.co/100", class: "img-fluid object-fit-contain h-100", alt: "Placeholder for #{partner['name']}"

              / Name & acronym underneath
              %h6.fw-semibold.mb-1.text-break= partner['name']
              - if partner['acronym']
                %p.text-muted.small.mb-0= partner['acronym']